that changed in my day to day life was how much of what I was putting in my 
body. I cannot stress the importance of hydrating. Not easy at first but in

body weight. For reference: I was a 34 year old man starting at 265 lbs. In

off coarse for a bit and now I am back at 245 lbs at 38 years old. No time 
like the present to get back on that horse.

replyContent: Hi Robert, Easy fix!  The last screen of the setup wizard gives you the option to select your Current Day - by selecting your Start Date.
